subject: Q : JUNIT : Java.lang.IllegalAccessError
msgSnippet: Hi , I am writing six test methods in a Test class. While compiling it is giving me this error Java.lang.IllegalAccessError ... superclass
messageBody:
Hi ,
I am writing six test methods in a Test class.

While compiling it is giving me this error Java.lang.IllegalAccessError
: class <sun.reflect.GeneratedConstructorAccessor5 cannot access its
superclass sun.reflect.ConstructorAccessorImpl>.

Please provide some pointer.

Thanks & rgds,
Vishal.
